māyājālābhisaṃbodhir nāma kramas tasya yathāhaṃ lābhī bhavāmi tathā bhagavān prakāśayatv iti vakṣyamāṇena kriyāpadena saṃbandhaḥ | |

<commentary>ajñānapaṅkamagnānāṃ sarvasattvānāṃ hitāya ca | tatrājñānam avidyā saivāsaṅgasthānatvād duruttaratvāc ca paṅka iva paṅkaḥ | tasmin magnā ye satvās teṣām hitāya || punar api kiṃviśiṣṭās te sattvā ity āha kleśavyākulacetasaḥ | kleśā ṣaṭ | tathā cāhābhidharme |

	mānadṛgvicikitsāś ca rāgapratighamūḍhayaḥ |

iti || taiḥ kleśair vyākulāni cetāṃsi yeṣāṃ sattvānāṃ te kleśavyākulacetasaḥ | atas teṣām || anuttaraphalaprāptaye bhagavān prakāśayatv iti tadarthaṃ tatprāptaya iti ||
</commentary>

prakāśayatu bhagavān ity āha | saṃbuddha iti śāśvatadvāreṇa | |